pullRequest.title: CDPCP-1941. Fix cloud identity sync filter
pullRequest.bodyText:
CloudIdentitySyncService was filtering by the identity domain, but
this field may be null. This is fixed by filtering based on cloud
identity name instead. This commit also adds unit tests for
CloudIdentitySyncService.

nodes.bodyText: Should we use Objects.equals for this to be safe? The current code assumes that the fields are not null. I see the fields are annotated @NotNull, but that just affects validation.

commit.message:
CDPCP-1941. Fix cloud identity sync filter

CloudIdentitySyncService was filtering by the identity domain, but
this field may be null. This is fixed by filtering based on cloud
identity name instead. This commit also adds unit tests for
CloudIdentitySyncService.
